  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA49">
<l>arāvi vaḷaittaṉaiya vaṅkuḻavit tiṅkaḷ</l>
<l>virāvu katirviriyavōṭi - virāvutalāl</l>
<l>poṉṉōṭu veḷḷip puripurintāṟ pōlāvē</l>
<l>taṉṉōṭē yoppāṉ caṭai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pretty calf moon that is like something polished [and] curved,</l>
<l>running to expand mixed rays, is it not</l>
<l>as if one made a thread of silver with gold by mixture,</l>
<l>on the matted hair of him who is equal only to himself?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
